#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: bench-list-ops
description: map + filter + fold over a List — exercises collection dispatch.
---

# List ops

```scalascript
val n  = 100000
val t0 = nanoTime()

val xs     = List.range(0, n)
val result = xs.map(x => x * 2).filter(x => x % 3 == 0).foldLeft(0L)((a, x) => a + x)

val t1 = nanoTime()

println(s"BENCH_MS: ${(t1 - t0) / 1000000}")
println(s"result=$result")
```
